    rdfs:label "Temperature T2 / degC"@en ;
    qudt:hasQuantityKind quantitykind:Temperature ;
    rdfs:comment "Temperature recorded by auxiliary temperature channel 2 of the test setup, in degree Celsius. Sensor placement (e.g. cell surface, terminal, or elsewhere) is setup-defined and not constrained by this term; record the placement in accompanying metadata. Where a channel is known to measure the surface temperature of the test object, see also surface_temperature_celsius."@en ;
